{"doc":" 知识库文档实体，对应 kb_documents 表。\n\n <p>表示知识库中的单个文档，记录文档的元信息、处理状态和检索统计。\n 文档上传后经过分块处理，用于 AI 检索增强。</p>\n","fields":[{"name":"id","doc":"主键ID "},{"name":"kbId","doc":"所属知识库ID "},{"name":"title","doc":"文档标题 "},{"name":"fileType","doc":"文件类型：pdf / docx / md 等 "},{"name":"filePath","doc":"文件存储路径 "},{"name":"fileSize","doc":"文件大小（字节） "},{"name":"chunkCount","doc":"分块数量 "},{"name":"hitCount","doc":"被检索命中次数 "},{"name":"injectMode","doc":"注入方式：AUTO_INJECT / ON_DEMAND / DISABLED "},{"name":"refProjects","doc":"被引用的项目数 "},{"name":"status","doc":"处理状态：PENDING（待处理）/ PROCESSING（处理中）/ READY（就绪）/ ERROR（出错） "},{"name":"errorMessage","doc":"处理错误信息 "},{"name":"uploadedBy","doc":"上传者用户ID "},{"name":"createdAt","doc":"创建时间 "},{"name":"updatedAt","doc":"最后更新时间 "}],"enumConstants":[],"methods":[],"constructors":[]}